

  * Install Apache et mod_dav

  * adduser www-data ovd-fs
  
  * mkdir /var/spool/ulteo/ovd/
  * chown ovd-fs:ovd-fs /var/spool/ulteo/ovd/

  * push config apache <<EOF
DAVMinTimeout 600
DAVDepthInfinity On

Alias /ovd/fs /var/lib/ulteo/ovd/fs
<Directory /var/lib/ulteo/ovd/fs>
     DAV on
     AuthNAme "WebDAV Storage"
     AuthType Basic
     AuthUserFile /var/spool/ulteo/ovd/fs.dav.passwd
     Require valid-user
     AllowOverride AuthConfig Limit
</Directory>
EOF

  * restart apache
  